  "title": "Production Specialist (Tuas)",
  "description": "<p><p><strong>Job Post: Production Specialist (Tuas)</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Optimize Performance:</strong> Operate, calibrate, and fine-tune machinery for reliable, top-tier output.</p></li><li><p><strong>Prevent Downtime:</strong> Conduct proactive maintenance, spotting potential issues before they become problems.</p></li><li><p><strong>Solve Issues:</strong> Diagnose and repair faults across mechanical, electrical, and automated systems with precision.</p></li><li><p><strong>Safety:</strong> Rigorously test and maintain all safety systems to protect yourself and the team.</p></li><li><p><strong>Drive Improvement:</strong> Maintain accurate logs and documentation to help us continuously work smarter.</p></li><li><p><strong>Expertise:</strong> Empower equipment operators with technical knowledge for safe and confident daily use.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>A minimum of 3 years of hands-on experience in a manufacturing or production environment.</p></li><li><p>Proven skill in troubleshooting, diagnostics, and making precise mechanical adjustments.</p></li><li><p>A strong advantage if you have experience with PLC-controlled systems or electrical repair. (We provide training for the right person!)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Schedule & Rewards</strong></p><p>We believe in predictable work that respects your life.<br />Day Shift: 7:30 AM – 7:30 PM<br />Night Shift: 7:30 PM – 7:30 AM</p><ul><li><p>Choose a pattern that fits you: Work <strong>4, 5, or 6 days</strong> per week.</p></li><li><p>We provide <strong>1 meal break and 2 tea breaks</strong> daily.</p></li></ul></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
